thub.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/23083) (rpc: Fail to return undocumented or misdocumented JSON by MarcoFalke)\n* [#22838](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22838) (descriptors: Be able to specify change and receiving in a single descriptor string by achow101)\n* [#22807](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22807) (RPC: Add universal options argument to listtransactions by kristapsk)\n* [#22776](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22776) (rpc/wallet: add optional transaction(s) to getbalances by kallewoof)\n* [#22775](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22775) (rpc: Add option to list transactions from oldest to newest in `listtransactions` RPC command by ben-kaufman)\n* [#22751](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22751) (rpc/wallet: add simulaterawtransaction RPC by kallewoof)\n* [#22558](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22558) (psbt: Taproot fields for PSBT by achow101)\n* [#22514](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22514) (psbt: Actually use SIGHASH_DEFAULT for PSBT signing by achow101)\n* [#22341](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22341) (rpc: add getxpub by Sjors)\n* [#21928](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/21928) (wallet: allow toggling external_signer flag by Sjors)\n* [#21576](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/21576) (rpc, gui: bumpfee signer support by Sjors)\n* [#21283](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/21283) (Implement BIP 370 PSBTv2 by achow101)\n* [#20640](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/20640) (wallet, refactor: return out-params of CreateTransaction() as optional struct by theStack)\n* [#20583](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/20583) (rpc: Add missing BlockUntilSyncedToCurrentChain to wallet RPCs by MarcoFalke)\n* [#19602](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/19602) (wallet: Migrate legacy wallets to descriptor wallets by achow101)\n* [#14707](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/14707) ([RPC] Include coinbase transactions in receivedby RPCs by andrewtoth)\n\nIf you consid